<i>a century ago.</i>

334
00:31:18.979 --> 00:31:22.015
<i>seven people. including my</i>
<i>brother. have been murdered.</i>

335
00:31:34.662 --> 00:31:36.664
<i>I'm Frederick Loren.</i>

336
00:31:36.798 --> 00:31:39.133
<i>and I've rented the house</i>
<i>on Haunted Hill tonight</i>

337
00:31:39.266 --> 00:31:41.770
<i>so that my wife</i>
<i>can give a party.</i>

338
00:31:42.035 --> 00:31:45.205
<i>A haunted house party.</i>

339
00:31:45.372 --> 00:31:47.542
<i>She's so amusing.</i>

340
00:31:47.675 --> 00:31:51.311
