<i>a few murders.</i>

342
00:31:53.914 --> 00:31:55.850
<i>You're all invited.</i>

343
00:31:55.983 --> 00:31:58.986
<i>If any of you will spend</i>
<i>the next 12 hours in this house.</i>

344
00:31:59.119 --> 00:32:01.723
