I'm sorry.

425
00:36:57.384 --> 00:36:59.153
It's just he took you
all the time.

426
00:36:59.286 --> 00:37:00.220
I just thought--

427
00:37:00.353 --> 00:37:01.622
No. no. it's fine. I understand.

428
00:37:01.756 --> 00:37:03.423
It's just. um...

429
