490
00:43:21.502 --> 00:43:24.338
Okay! Do it then.

491
00:43:24.472 --> 00:43:25.706
Let's go.

492
00:43:27.141 --> 00:43:29.210
Don't just fucking stand there.

493
00:43:29.343 --> 00:43:30.244
Do something.

494
00:43:30.377 --> 00:43:32.179
Cut--
Cut me open!

495
00:43:33.180 --> 00:43:34.849
