505
00:46:38.399 --> 00:46:39.734
Shit.

506
00:47:09.897 --> 00:47:11.700
Maddie!

507
00:48:23.937 --> 00:48:27.776
Hey! Hey! JC it's me. JC.

508
00:48:27.908 --> 00:48:31.546
It's me. JC! Stop!

509
00:48:34.649 --> 00:48:38.352
